title: Freddy Gall for OJ Wheels!
description:
Keep it crusty with Freddy Gall! Fred Gall has been stacking some footage with the homies out on the Right Coast, and holding it down for the Scum League. Enjoy over two and a half minutes of fresh off the press clips of Freddy for OJ Wheels. Be sure to check out his new 56mm "Getoz" as well...Cheers.
@freddygall

Music:
CURS
